text.tspan: - allow swagger-json url to be changed
- allow swagger-ui operation to appear in multiple tags
- merge files lib.* into standaalone file assets.swgg.rollup.js
- add spec-compliant collectionFormat parameter for arrays
- fix shBuildDoc accidentally adding coverage to doc
- merge utility2 and swgg namespace into local namespace
- revamp user-login / user-logout to use standard json-web-encryption token
- temporary fix for chrome render bug - https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=66\
- migrate db from nedb-lite to db-lite
- allow file export / import of nedb-database
- migrate nedb-api from swagger-lite to utility2
- rename collectDoc to dbRow and collection to dbTable
- replace lib bcrypt and lib cryptojs with lib sjcl
- fix internal tests for heroku backend
- deploy standalone app to heroku test-server
- add 'run internal test' button in webpage
- add env var npm_config_mode_backend to disable utility2.serverLocalUrlTest
- ui - add button to reset nedb database
- move all swagger-backend-config into top-level swagger-property 'x-swgg-apiDict'
- replace swagger-tools dependency with function swgg.validateBySwagger
- add extra constraints to function swgg.collectDocListRandomCreate
- ui - input element's valueEncoded can only be '', null, or undefined
- fix bug when a document's id is zero
- remove Backbone, Handlebars, and jQuery dependencies from lib.swagger-ui.js
- enable multiple api endpoints with same operationId, but unique keyUnique
- merge api crudCreateOrUpdateOne and crudCreateOrUpdateOneByKeyUnique into crudUpdateOneByKeyUn\
- encode arrays as json-string in query-param
- fix 0 statusCode in userLoginByPassword and userLogout api
- split swgg.middlewareValidate into swgg.middlewareRouter and swgg.middlewareValidate
- merge collection BuiltinFile into collection TestModelCrud in example.js
- merge collection BuiltinUser into collection User in example.js
- fix Uncaught TypeError: this.trigger is not a function
- add function swgg.collectDocRandomCreate to create random collectDoc
- cleanup Backbone and Handlebars in lib.swagger-ui.js
- move request.swgg* objects to namespace request.swgg
- admin-ui - fix datatables crashing when rows are empty
- allow jsonapi's response.data to be an empty array
- add '_Builtin' prefix to swagger-lite's builtin swagger-definition names
- do not send readonly properties in swgg.apiDict clients
- in swgg.validateByPropertyDef, add regex pattern validation according to http://json-schema.or\
- consolidate browser state-init into jsonp call stateInit
- admin-ui - add swagger-form validation to form-inputs
- admin-ui - merge all dt state-info into swgg.dt object
- admin-ui - keyUnique crud operations can use arbitray keys, instead of only 'id' key
- admin-ui - add x-title option for rendering labels for swagger params and property inputs
- admin-ui - crud-keyUnique operations can depend on arbitrary unique-key (previously tied to 'i\
- add boolean/integer/number/string schema-properties as params in crudGetManyByQuery
- allow arbitrary name for body-param in local.swgg.middlewareCrud
- add 'x-notRequired' options to pathObject params to override 'required' option
- add 'x-validateUnusedDefinition' option in swgg.validateBySwagger to ignore unused definitions
- use jsonp to init default browser-state instead of with hard-coded template
- split index.js into index.js and lib.admin-ui.js
- admin-ui - hook utility2.assert and utility2.onErrorDefault with bootstrap alert;
- admin-ui - show swagger-property-type in thead / tfoot / form input
- swgg.apiUpdate will now error-log schema-validation-errors instead of throwing them
- move static assets to /external dir, which will be fetched during postinstall
- fix missing createdAt field in nedb update-replace
- add default-crud-api crudCreateOrReplaceMany, crudCreateOrUpdateOne, and crudCreateOrUpdateOne\
- keep internal nedb _id separate from mongodb id
- enable integer id's in default crud api
- add file index.css and rename asset swagger-ui.rollup.css to swagger-lite.css
- fix ui-wiggle for client-side validation error
- migrate live-test-server from heroku to github, with browser emulation of server
- revamp local._OperationPrototypeExecute to mock ajax request to browser-emulated server
- move most of node js-env code to shared js-env
- wiggle frontend input during validation error
